summary: SAVE AND RESTORE EQUIPMENT SETS WITH A KEYSTROKE
descriptionHtml:
Jaxonz Outfitter\'s Guide lets you easily define and equip outfits in Skyrim! Less tedium, more fun!
Even remembers and equips spells and shouts.
Define your own hotkeys for equipping sets in an instant.

Buy the Outfitter\'s Guide at Belethor\'s in Whiterun.. or you may find it laying around elsewhere

Presto! You\'re a quick change artist!

[THIS MOD HAS ADVANCED FEATURES REQUIRING SKSE (Skyrim Script Extender) http://skse.silverlock.org/ ]
author: Jaxonz
